---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
const frontmatter = {
  title: "The Future of AI Prompt Engineering",
  description: "Discover how MindScribe is revolutionizing the way we work with AI models.",
  date: "2024-03-05",
  author: "Alex Thompson",
  category: "Industry Insights",
  image: "https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1677442136019-21780ecad995?auto=format&fit=crop&q=80"
};
---

<Layout title={frontmatter.title}>
  <main class="pt-32 pb-24">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-6">
      <article class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <header class="text-center mb-16">
          <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-6">
            <span class="gradient-text">{frontmatter.title}</span>
          </h1>
          <div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-4 text-sm text-gray-400">
            <time datetime={frontmatter.date}>{new Date(frontmatter.date).toLocaleDateString('en-US', { month: 'long', day: 'numeric', year: 'numeric' })}</time>
            <span>•</span>
            <span>{frontmatter.category}</span>
            <span>•</span>
            <span>{frontmatter.author}</span>
          </div>
        </header>

        <div class="prose lg:prose-xl max-w-none">
          <img 
            src={frontmatter.image} 
            alt={frontmatter.title}
            class="w-full rounded-2xl mb-12 aspect-[2/1] object-cover"
          />

          <p class="lead text-xl text-gray-600 mb-8">
            As AI technologies continue to evolve, the art and science of prompt engineering have become critical in unlocking the full potential of intelligent systems.
          </p>

          <section class="my-10">
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold mb-4">Introducing MindScribe</h2>
            <p>
              MindScribe represents a quantum leap in AI interaction, providing developers and researchers with a sophisticated platform to craft, optimize, and manage AI prompts with unprecedented precision and efficiency.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section class="my-10">
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold mb-4">Key Innovations</h2>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6">
              <li>Advanced prompt template library</li>
              <li>Real-time prompt performance analytics</li>
              <li>Collaborative prompt development environment</li>
              <li>AI-assisted prompt optimization</li>
              <li>Version control for prompt iterations</li>
            </ul>
          </section>

          <section class="my-10">
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold mb-4">The Evolving Landscape</h2>
            <p>
              Prompt engineering is no longer just about crafting input text. It's a sophisticated discipline that requires understanding context, model behavior, and the nuanced art of communication with AI systems.
            </p>
          </section>

          <div class="mt-12 text-center">
            <a href="/blog" class="bg-blue-600 text-white px-6 py-3 rounded-lg hover:bg-blue-700 transition-colors">
              Back to Our Blogs
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </article>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>